name: Steampunk Fob-style LED Light Brooch (rounded square setting)
description:
STEAMPUNK FOB-STYLE LED LIGHT BROOCH (rounded square setting)

Wear on your clothing, scarf or bag.  This brooch is a fun and quirky way to increase your visibility and style up your ride!  A great gift for any bike-riding enthusiast!

► Natural Mahogany wooden brooch featuring vintage-inspired bicycle images printed on ivory fabric and set in resin

► Antique brass chain links to fob in tweed with LED light

► LED light component comes with 3 replaceable button cell batteries with a battery-life of continuous use for 420+ bike-riding hours!

► Vibrant flashing LED light can easily be seen from a long distance and flashes red and blue

► Twist clockwise to turn light on, twist anti-clockwise to turn light off

► Replacement batteries available from www.thevamptheveilandthevicarshop.bigcartel.com
 
*Please keep in mind this brooch is primarily an accessory and should be used in addition to standard front and rear bicycle lights

...........................................................................................

MADE IN MELBOURNE, AUSTRALIA
